@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #78671 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?

I was able to reproduce with code that's a little more sensible and more likely to be something someone would write: https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/78671#issuecomment-749067604 Not sure if this is P-high. It seems this was added to the 1.49 milestone
Pretty sure this shouldn't be P-high: the feature is experimental, and it says so before it crashes.
